{"tid":674772,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［開飯喇］銀龍我屌你老母","createTime":"2018-05-23T04:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T05:39:12.000Z","uid":96628,"like":22,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"67e0ac7e04936605b26e325619e0013eee6f3c3a","tid":674772,"uid":96628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:05:02.000Z","msg":"話說小妹我外賣叫早餐，叫返鋪頭，<br />\n個收銀態度已經差，語氣差加cut人線，<br />\n屌你老母電話又唔撚講幾錢，打返去無人聽，<br />\n一到來$42，我比$60話無錢找<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我屌你個老母，我打返去好聲子氣問話有冇得落來找返；<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好意思，岩岩有個外賣你地無錢找比我，我可唔可以晏少少落來找返錢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽唔到呀！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （重複）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩呀，啲錢係佢架！（想收我線）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  喂？唔好意思，好似你地無錢找比我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩話？哦～佢話啲錢係比佢架喎，得啦幫你追<br />\nCut撚左線<br />\n<br />\n屌你全家，我已經好聲好氣自己落來拎返，<br />\n戇撚鳩好似我做錯事咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係錢嘅問題，十幾蚊，<br />\n你好聲好氣話走左無得計，怕有誤會又好乜柒都好，<br />\n仲理直氣壯話啲錢係你嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母死全家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n謝斐道銀龍等比隔離龍城收你皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/1360948487.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F01%2F1360948487.jpg&h=3c172ba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/24/044543_db71dd7447fe92851a1acbcc6b8d2899.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F24%2F044543_db71dd7447fe92851a1acbcc6b8d2899.jpg&h=afdec42e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/23/120413_2c473cc7c32f567fe91aa440f24fb40e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F23%2F120413_2c473cc7c32f567fe91aa440f24fb40e.png&h=90a92dbe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14c2c41e023297ca9db4283b0bbfcb5b6f265397","tid":674772,"uid":16061,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:08:03.000Z","msg":"戇鳩 佢無得找你咪唔好要"},{"pid":"e96a1711af39ae055967c9d757be5390c4712c0d","tid":674772,"uid":53554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:08:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6027dba8d3d87aebd7e45775264a9bf7bd52e412","tid":674772,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e96a1711af39ae055967c9d757be5390c4712c0d","tid":674772,"uid":53554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:08:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:10:17.000Z","msg":"屌你咩，網名覆咗啦，仲駛留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49654ddcf13a3c21a463a086a850c27c62c421d4","tid":674772,"uid":63588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:11:05.000Z","msg":"俾人撚到咁仲要好聲好氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6822fc38afa738e68184bafa5192f7955d78e2f","tid":674772,"uid":96628,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"14c2c41e023297ca9db4283b0bbfcb5b6f265397","tid":674772,"uid":16061,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:08:03.000Z","msg":"戇鳩 佢無得找你咪唔好要"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T04:32:19.000Z","msg":"唔好咁浪費啲野食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7cab39ee3a721423dfcc8c7a96c9f15733c150","tid":674772,"uid":966